<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ghastly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ghastly,</orth> ghostlike, dismal, horrible: <cit><quote>some g. sprite,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 451" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 451</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>g. shadows,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 451" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 451</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>in g. night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 27.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 27, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this g. looking,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.309" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 309</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 5, 8</bibl>. <cit><quote>g., gaping wounds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.212" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 212</bibl></cit> (Pistol's speech). <cit><quote>g. dreams,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.3" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 3</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>fearful</emph>). <cit><quote>g. women,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 1.3.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 3, 23</bibl></cit>.<lb />Adverbially: <cit><quote>staring full g. like a strangled man,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 170</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>